creator: Erich Leinsdorf
description:
Many people know John Judge from his work in assassination research, but he did much more than that. This is a brief look at some of the other work of his.

Mr. Maresca and Mr. Judge discussed conscientious objector status and how it is achieved. The guests discussed the history of conscientious objection and the status of conscientious objectors in the Persian Gulf War.

*John Judge*
Counselor

*Charles Maresca*
Attorney
